data.description:
Adorable Remodeled Brick home located right of Business  190 in Copperas Cove! Located near restaurants , shopping , groceries and more! The recently remodeled home offers 3 spacious bedrooms, and 2 remodeled bathrooms.  Large living room which follows into a dining area , and a galley kitchen.  Kitchen has all new cabinets, counter tops, and appliances !   Master bath has a newly tiled shower tub combo.  You will be happy to find larger than normal size closets nestled in each bedroom. Newer flooring thru out home, New Hot water heater and HVAC unit.  Dont miss your chance on this adorable home. 
Sit on your back patio and enjoy the extra space between neighbors for tad bit more privacy.   Large Mature tree in front yard will offer plenty of shade in the spring and summer seasons.   You have a puppy, great , the yard is completely fenced and waiting for you to move in ! Call your favorite realtor today for a private showing !
